<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Prematurely optimizing (Posty o numba)</title><link>https://stanczakdominik.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://stanczakdominik.github.io/pl/categories/numba.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>pl</language><copyright>Contents © 2021 &lt;a href="https://matrix.to/#/@StanczakDominik:matrix.org"&gt;Dominik Stańczak&lt;/a&gt; 
